Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:23.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on! On a journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:25.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,ねぇ 知りたいでしょう？
